Package chirptask.google

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CalendarController
    CalendarController is the main controller that interacts with Google Calendar.
    CalendarHandler  
    ConcurrentDelete
    ConcurrentDeleted is submitted to the ExecutorService to run Concurrently It will determine which method to call based on the Task Type Then, it will delete the correct task with the stored Google ID.
    DateTimeHandler
    DateTimeHandler is a class that contains static methods to help parse dates from input (assumed to be formatted before reaching here) into a Google DateTime object used by the relevant Google API.
    GoogleAuthorizer
    GoogleAuthorizer provides a static method to authorize ChirpTask to perform the Google Service calls on behalf of the user by authenticating via OAuth2.0.
    GoogleController
    GoogleController is the main component that interacts with the Google Services.
    TasksController
    TasksController is the main controller that interacts with Google Tasks.
